<h2>

  <a name="suche-allgemein"></a>



    How can I use the full text search option?

  </h2>



<p>The archive has a full text search in which you can enter one or more search terms. </p>

<p>Several search terms are linked with AND.</p>
<p>Example:</p>
<p>On a search with the entry Auschwitz Mauthausen, all interviews in which both terms occur will be found. If you only
  enter one of the two terms, you will obtain more results.</p>
<p></p>







